  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3022055">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3022055/" class="title-link">科学的哲学解释</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3022055"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/piggyofdarkness/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1529628-12.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/piggyofdarkness/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">已注销的冻冻猪</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-02-28"
      class="main-meta">2010-02-28 12:54:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3022055_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                         石里克给自然哲学下的定义是：自然哲学的任务就是解释自然科学命题的意义。     而他认为精确的知识就是那种按照逻辑的原则可以完全表达清楚的知识。因此在这本书中他分析了自然科学中各个基本概念的意义，给自然科学下了精确的逻辑定义。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3022055_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3022055_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





